WEBVTT
X-TIMESTAMP-MAP=MPEGTS:900000,LOCAL:00:00:00.000

00:00:16.850 --> 00:00:18.309 position:50% align:center
[JAIL gasps]

00:00:18.393 --> 00:00:20.937 position:50% align:center
Is that the demon?

00:00:31.781 --> 00:00:33.533 position:50% align:center
No way.

00:00:33.616 --> 00:00:37.787 position:50% align:center
How is it still able to fly?
And what is it doing here?

00:00:42.876 --> 00:00:44.878 position:50% align:center
[HINA gasps]

00:00:44.961 --> 00:00:46.755 position:50% align:center
[BOTH gasp]

00:00:53.428 --> 00:00:55.972 position:50% align:center
What the hell... is that thing?

00:00:57.432 --> 00:00:58.850 position:50% align:center
[gasps]

00:01:00.435 --> 00:01:02.270 position:50% align:center
[TOWNSPEOPLE scream]

00:01:16.826 --> 00:01:18.536 position:50% align:center
[JAIL]
I don't understand.

00:01:18.620 --> 00:01:22.457 position:50% align:center
Did that thing attack us...
with flashes of light?

00:01:24.209 --> 00:01:26.586 position:50% align:center
[gasps]

00:01:26.670 --> 00:01:28.338 position:50% align:center
Here it comes again!

00:01:29.923 --> 00:01:31.591 position:50% align:center
[LYNN, JAIL gasp]

00:01:34.761 --> 00:01:35.970 position:50% align:center
[LICHT]
Look out!

00:03:14.402 --> 00:03:16.363 position:50% align:center
Were there any casualties?

00:03:20.575 --> 00:03:22.702 position:50% align:center
No. Thanks to you.

00:03:29.084 --> 00:03:30.251 position:50% align:center
Good.

00:03:30.335 --> 00:03:31.795 position:50% align:center
Everybody, listen up!

00:03:31.878 --> 00:03:35.382 position:50% align:center
Right now, avoid that thing
like your lives depend on it!

00:03:35.465 --> 00:03:37.676 position:50% align:center
Knights, initiate an
immediate evacuation!

00:03:37.759 --> 00:03:39.969 position:50% align:center
I want you to get these
people underground!

00:03:40.053 --> 00:03:43.139 position:50% align:center
And, Jail! The second that
thing faces us, make a wall!

00:03:43.223 --> 00:03:46.184 position:50% align:center
As thick as you possibly can!
It's our only defense.

00:03:46.267 --> 00:03:49.187 position:50% align:center
That's enough! Where do you
get off taking my command?

00:03:49.270 --> 00:03:51.481 position:50% align:center
I know how to fight it,
so I'm calling the shots!

00:03:51.564 --> 00:03:53.650 position:50% align:center
People's lives are
at stake here!

00:03:53.733 --> 00:03:56.194 position:50% align:center
[gasps]

00:03:56.277 --> 00:03:58.238 position:50% align:center
Does this make any difference?

00:04:00.490 --> 00:04:02.534 position:50% align:center
[gasps]

00:04:02.617 --> 00:04:04.577 position:50% align:center
If those are real, then he's a--

00:04:04.661 --> 00:04:06.037 position:50% align:center
Colonel.

00:04:12.627 --> 00:04:16.256 position:50% align:center
[TOWNSPEOPLE shouting]

00:04:16.339 --> 00:04:19.009 position:50% align:center
Just leave this
"Demon of the Abyss" to me.

00:04:22.429 --> 00:04:24.848 position:50% align:center
[JAIL] The idiot I've been
chasing this entire time

00:04:24.931 --> 00:04:27.892 position:50% align:center
is a colonel? Impossible.

00:04:34.190 --> 00:04:35.859 position:50% align:center
[JAIL]
The report said he was an Ace,

00:04:35.942 --> 00:04:38.236 position:50% align:center
and Aces were heroes
of the Waste War.

00:04:38.319 --> 00:04:40.030 position:50% align:center
That could explain his rank.

00:04:42.115 --> 00:04:43.950 position:50% align:center
[JAIL] But that would also
mean the rumors about him

00:04:44.034 --> 00:04:47.245 position:50% align:center
being a Legendary Ace
were actually true!

00:04:47.328 --> 00:04:50.248 position:50% align:center
[LICHT grunts]
I told you all to evacuate!

00:04:50.331 --> 00:04:52.500 position:50% align:center
Go now while I have
its attention!

00:04:54.753 --> 00:04:55.795 position:50% align:center
You heard the man!

00:04:55.879 --> 00:04:57.922 position:50% align:center
[TOWNSPEOPLE shouting]

00:04:58.006 --> 00:05:00.050 position:50% align:center
Women and children first!
Let's go!

00:05:00.133 --> 00:05:02.302 position:50% align:center
[KNIGHT B]
This way! Hurry!

00:05:02.385 --> 00:05:04.637 position:50% align:center
[TOWNSBOY A cries]

00:05:04.721 --> 00:05:05.722 position:50% align:center
[HINA]
Are you hurt?

00:05:05.805 --> 00:05:08.641 position:50% align:center
Everyone! Remain calm!

00:05:13.605 --> 00:05:14.814 position:50% align:center
[HINA gasps]

00:05:28.912 --> 00:05:30.830 position:50% align:center
Go... Come on!

00:05:30.914 --> 00:05:31.831 position:50% align:center
Come on!

00:05:31.915 --> 00:05:33.083 position:50% align:center
He's got this!

00:05:33.166 --> 00:05:34.584 position:50% align:center
You think?

00:05:35.960 --> 00:05:39.464 position:50% align:center
[HINA]
Go, Licht! You can do it!

00:05:48.682 --> 00:05:50.517 position:50% align:center
[LICHT shouts]

00:05:57.107 --> 00:05:58.900 position:50% align:center
Althing's here.

00:05:58.983 --> 00:06:00.527 position:50% align:center
What's that mean?

00:06:00.610 --> 00:06:01.945 position:50% align:center
[LYNN]
Althing?

00:06:02.028 --> 00:06:03.780 position:50% align:center
That's what members of the
military call those long,

00:06:03.863 --> 00:06:05.782 position:50% align:center
black hands.

00:06:05.865 --> 00:06:07.867 position:50% align:center
[grunts]

00:06:07.951 --> 00:06:10.120 position:50% align:center
[PELE] Yeah, the literal
hands of judgment,

00:06:10.203 --> 00:06:12.038 position:50% align:center
AKA the "supreme assembly."

00:06:12.122 --> 00:06:14.082 position:50% align:center
They supposedly decide
everything that happens

00:06:14.165 --> 00:06:17.127 position:50% align:center
in Alcia, including who
gets sent to the Abyss,

00:06:17.210 --> 00:06:19.254 position:50% align:center
though I don't know
much more than that.

00:06:26.177 --> 00:06:28.096 position:50% align:center
Are they going after the demon?

00:06:28.179 --> 00:06:30.557 position:50% align:center
[LYNN] So they actually
came to help us?

00:06:34.978 --> 00:06:37.564 position:50% align:center
[PELE]
Damn! They can't reach it!

00:06:45.280 --> 00:06:46.489 position:50% align:center
[LICHT grunts]

00:06:51.870 --> 00:06:53.830 position:50% align:center
[grunts]

00:06:56.499 --> 00:06:58.585 position:50% align:center
[HINA] Why did Licht
become their target?

00:06:58.668 --> 00:07:02.630 position:50% align:center
Get too close, and Althing
will automatically attack you.

00:07:02.714 --> 00:07:04.591 position:50% align:center
Not even he stands a chance.

00:07:04.674 --> 00:07:06.051 position:50% align:center
[HINA]
No...

00:07:17.979 --> 00:07:19.564 position:50% align:center
[LICHT grunts]

00:07:19.647 --> 00:07:22.484 position:50% align:center
Move it! I don't
have time for you!

00:07:28.948 --> 00:07:31.368 position:50% align:center
[gasps]
Not again! Not now!

00:07:31.451 --> 00:07:35.372 position:50% align:center
[JAIL gasps]
"Again"? Is this common?

00:07:35.455 --> 00:07:37.540 position:50% align:center
I wouldn't say it was common.

00:07:37.624 --> 00:07:41.836 position:50% align:center
But it has happened before, when
he struck one of those hands.

00:07:41.920 --> 00:07:45.382 position:50% align:center
[LICHT groans]

00:07:46.716 --> 00:07:47.926 position:50% align:center
[HINA]
Licht?

00:07:49.177 --> 00:07:51.888 position:50% align:center
Please say something.
Can you--?

00:07:58.269 --> 00:08:01.022 position:50% align:center
One thing I know for sure is
that he can't fight like this!

00:08:01.106 --> 00:08:02.273 position:50% align:center
Please, save him!

00:08:02.357 --> 00:08:03.858 position:50% align:center
--[JAIL] I can't.
--[HINA] What?

00:08:03.942 --> 00:08:06.236 position:50% align:center
[JAIL] It's against the law for
members of the military

00:08:06.319 --> 00:08:07.654 position:50% align:center
to attack Althing.

00:08:07.737 --> 00:08:10.031 position:50% align:center
If we were to assist him now,

00:08:10.115 --> 00:08:13.410 position:50% align:center
we would be court martialed
and face the ultimate penalty.

00:08:13.493 --> 00:08:14.911 position:50% align:center
Execution.

00:08:14.994 --> 00:08:17.580 position:50% align:center
[LICHT grunts]

00:08:17.664 --> 00:08:19.165 position:50% align:center
You'd die?

00:08:27.173 --> 00:08:28.466 position:50% align:center
That's so cruel!

00:08:28.550 --> 00:08:30.552 position:50% align:center
Interfering would be
a death wish.

00:08:30.635 --> 00:08:33.346 position:50% align:center
Althing is too big
of a target to miss.

00:08:33.430 --> 00:08:35.890 position:50% align:center
Since we can't help him
without breaking the law,

00:08:35.974 --> 00:08:37.767 position:50% align:center
we can't help him period.

00:08:37.851 --> 00:08:41.813 position:50% align:center
So you're just gonna stand there
and let Licht fight by himself?

00:08:43.940 --> 00:08:48.111 position:50% align:center
[LICHT groans]

00:08:49.654 --> 00:08:52.824 position:50% align:center
[LICHT] History won't
repeat itself! I won't let it!

00:08:56.786 --> 00:08:58.538 position:50% align:center
[gasps]

00:09:00.957 --> 00:09:03.543 position:50% align:center
[gasps]
Licht!

00:09:03.626 --> 00:09:05.045 position:50% align:center
[NANA]
Stop, Hina!

00:09:05.128 --> 00:09:07.297 position:50% align:center
Going to him now wouldn't help,
you'd be holding him back!

00:09:07.380 --> 00:09:10.550 position:50% align:center
Yeah, but I can't
just abandon him!

00:09:10.633 --> 00:09:14.220 position:50% align:center
[grunts]

00:09:14.304 --> 00:09:16.806 position:50% align:center
[JAIL]
He's a dead man either way.

00:09:16.890 --> 00:09:17.974 position:50% align:center
He attacked Althing.

00:09:18.058 --> 00:09:19.392 position:50% align:center
[HINA]
It's not fair!

00:09:19.476 --> 00:09:21.936 position:50% align:center
He's trying so hard
to protect us!

00:09:22.020 --> 00:09:25.482 position:50% align:center
He's risking his life
for the entire town!

00:09:25.565 --> 00:09:29.694 position:50% align:center
And you're saying he'll die...
for doing the right thing?

00:09:29.778 --> 00:09:31.696 position:50% align:center
Uh, sir? I, um...

00:09:31.780 --> 00:09:35.033 position:50% align:center
Drop it, Lynn. You know
the law as well as I do.

00:09:36.368 --> 00:09:37.702 position:50% align:center
But, sir!

00:09:37.786 --> 00:09:41.456 position:50% align:center
[JAIL] Hmm, that's odd.
I must've misplaced my glasses.

00:09:41.539 --> 00:09:46.044 position:50% align:center
[LYNN] Huh? What? Misplaced?
They're in your hand.

00:09:46.127 --> 00:09:47.587 position:50% align:center
[JAIL]
Such a shame.

00:09:47.671 --> 00:09:51.341 position:50% align:center
Because without them,
I can't see a thing.

00:09:51.424 --> 00:09:54.928 position:50% align:center
Wait! First Lieutenant!
Is this happening?

00:10:00.517 --> 00:10:01.726 position:50% align:center
[BOTH gasp]

00:10:18.410 --> 00:10:20.954 position:50% align:center
[grunts]

00:10:21.037 --> 00:10:21.996 position:50% align:center
Thanks, Jail.

00:10:22.080 --> 00:10:23.748 position:50% align:center
You're... insane!

00:10:23.832 --> 00:10:26.334 position:50% align:center
Just breaking the law
without a care in the world!

00:10:26.418 --> 00:10:28.503 position:50% align:center
[JAIL] Oh, is there something
there that would cause me

00:10:28.586 --> 00:10:32.007 position:50% align:center
to break the law?
My vision's a little blurry.

00:10:33.174 --> 00:10:35.635 position:50% align:center
[JAIL]
Lynn! Hurry and find my glasses!

00:10:35.719 --> 00:10:39.556 position:50% align:center
[gasps]
I would if I could.

00:10:42.058 --> 00:10:44.728 position:50% align:center
[LYNN]
But... It's the strangest thing.

00:10:44.811 --> 00:10:47.814 position:50% align:center
My sight suddenly
got just as bad!

00:10:47.897 --> 00:10:50.150 position:50% align:center
No! It happened to me, too!

00:10:50.233 --> 00:10:54.571 position:50% align:center
[PELE] Aw! Not funny, guys!
Who turned out the lights?

00:10:54.654 --> 00:10:56.114 position:50% align:center
Thank you all.

00:10:58.658 --> 00:11:00.326 position:50% align:center
[JAIL]
Pay attention.

00:11:14.466 --> 00:11:15.800 position:50% align:center
[JAIL]
Hmph...

00:11:18.511 --> 00:11:20.597 position:50% align:center
[shouts]

00:11:20.680 --> 00:11:22.724 position:50% align:center
[JAIL]
Annihilate that thing, Licht!

00:11:25.393 --> 00:11:26.603 position:50% align:center
[gasps]

00:11:26.686 --> 00:11:28.396 position:50% align:center
[gasps]

00:11:31.608 --> 00:11:34.486 position:50% align:center
[gasps]

00:11:34.569 --> 00:11:36.988 position:50% align:center
Hey! Why'd you stop your attack?

00:11:46.373 --> 00:11:49.000 position:50% align:center
[gasps]

00:11:49.084 --> 00:11:50.293 position:50% align:center
[gasps]

00:11:57.217 --> 00:11:58.968 position:50% align:center
--[gasps]
--[gun clicks]

00:12:02.847 --> 00:12:06.101 position:50% align:center
Long time no see, Commander.

00:12:06.184 --> 00:12:09.145 position:50% align:center
Yeah. Not long enough.

00:12:09.229 --> 00:12:10.772 position:50% align:center
[HINA]
Huh?

00:12:10.855 --> 00:12:12.232 position:50% align:center
Who are you? Tell me right n--

00:12:12.315 --> 00:12:13.817 position:50% align:center
[gunshot]

00:12:18.738 --> 00:12:20.573 position:50% align:center
[JAIL exhales]

00:12:23.368 --> 00:12:25.954 position:50% align:center
[grunts]

00:12:26.037 --> 00:12:27.539 position:50% align:center
Jail, no!

00:12:27.622 --> 00:12:30.792 position:50% align:center
[exhales]

00:12:30.875 --> 00:12:32.502 position:50% align:center
[LICHT]
This can't be real!

00:12:36.881 --> 00:12:38.425 position:50% align:center
[LYNN, PELE]
Huh?

00:12:51.771 --> 00:12:53.732 position:50% align:center
C'mon! Hang in there!

00:12:53.815 --> 00:12:55.608 position:50% align:center
You're cute when
you're concerned.

00:12:55.692 --> 00:12:56.901 position:50% align:center
[grunts]

00:12:58.194 --> 00:13:03.616 position:50% align:center
Tell me, who are you?
And why'd you do that to him?

00:13:03.700 --> 00:13:06.161 position:50% align:center
[MIZUKA]
My name is Mizuka Sonohara.

00:13:06.244 --> 00:13:09.289 position:50% align:center
One of the Legendary Aces,
at your service.

00:13:11.041 --> 00:13:13.626 position:50% align:center
The Ace of Pursuit,
to be precise!

00:13:22.052 --> 00:13:23.720 position:50% align:center
That girl's an Ace?

00:13:23.803 --> 00:13:25.555 position:50% align:center
[PELE, LYNN gasp]

00:13:25.638 --> 00:13:27.015 position:50% align:center
[grunts]

00:13:29.267 --> 00:13:31.269 position:50% align:center
[MIZUKA] Could you people
pretend like everything you saw

00:13:31.353 --> 00:13:34.856 position:50% align:center
today was some crazy dream?
Keep it our little secret, okay?

00:13:34.939 --> 00:13:38.151 position:50% align:center
Or at least... Heh! That's what
I'd say if I could trust you.

00:13:38.234 --> 00:13:41.112 position:50% align:center
Which, obviously, I can't do!

00:13:41.196 --> 00:13:42.697 position:50% align:center
But I have a backup plan.

00:13:42.781 --> 00:13:45.450 position:50% align:center
[laughs] I... think I'll
just kill everyone

00:13:45.533 --> 00:13:47.118 position:50% align:center
and stop you from
talking ever again!

00:13:47.202 --> 00:13:49.245 position:50% align:center
Sonohara, stop!

00:13:49.329 --> 00:13:54.334 position:50% align:center
[TOWNSPEOPLE yell, groan]

00:13:56.211 --> 00:13:57.629 position:50% align:center
[LICHT grunts]

00:13:59.714 --> 00:14:00.924 position:50% align:center
[gasps]

00:14:02.592 --> 00:14:05.387 position:50% align:center
[MIZUKA] I missed you more
than you will ever know.

00:14:06.680 --> 00:14:08.264 position:50% align:center
[LICHT]
Sonohara...

00:14:10.517 --> 00:14:12.519 position:50% align:center
[whimpers]

00:14:12.602 --> 00:14:14.521 position:50% align:center
[LYNN]
Wha...?

00:14:14.604 --> 00:14:17.357 position:50% align:center
You have to stop
this right now!

00:14:17.440 --> 00:14:19.776 position:50% align:center
Shooting innocent
people is wrong!

00:14:21.486 --> 00:14:23.113 position:50% align:center
You understand?

00:14:25.490 --> 00:14:27.492 position:50% align:center
[MIZUKA] I will always
obey you, commander.

00:14:27.575 --> 00:14:29.494 position:50% align:center
That is what I understand.

00:14:29.577 --> 00:14:33.289 position:50% align:center
I will always obey that order
you gave me so very long ago.

00:14:33.373 --> 00:14:35.208 position:50% align:center
When you said to kill people.

00:14:36.501 --> 00:14:37.460 position:50% align:center
Don't shoot!

00:14:37.544 --> 00:14:39.212 position:50% align:center
--[KNIGHT L groans]
--[HINA gasps]

00:14:39.295 --> 00:14:42.048 position:50% align:center
[LICHT]
This is wrong... Stop!

00:14:42.132 --> 00:14:45.218 position:50% align:center
[MIZUKA] How is this wrong?
I listened to what you said.

00:14:45.301 --> 00:14:48.513 position:50% align:center
I took your advice and
I was able to change!

00:14:48.596 --> 00:14:50.056 position:50% align:center
I can kill people now!

00:14:50.140 --> 00:14:52.934 position:50% align:center
I can slaughter every last
one of them! Do you see?

00:14:53.018 --> 00:14:54.728 position:50% align:center
No. Please, stop!

00:14:54.811 --> 00:14:56.021 position:50% align:center
[MIZUKA]
The old me might've stopped,

00:14:56.104 --> 00:14:58.898 position:50% align:center
but I'm a whole new woman!

00:14:58.982 --> 00:15:00.275 position:50% align:center
I'll show you.

00:15:07.157 --> 00:15:09.868 position:50% align:center
I can imitate the way
you used to do it.

00:15:09.951 --> 00:15:14.330 position:50% align:center
With a mild demeanor, a calm
expression, and blinding speed.

00:15:14.414 --> 00:15:17.834 position:50% align:center
I'll gun them all down
with pure finesse.

00:15:17.917 --> 00:15:19.836 position:50% align:center
I respond to
positive reinforcement,

00:15:19.919 --> 00:15:22.672 position:50% align:center
so feel free to praise me!

00:15:22.756 --> 00:15:27.761 position:50% align:center
[TOWNSPEOPLE screaming]

00:15:31.973 --> 00:15:34.017 position:50% align:center
[LICHT]
Sonohara stop!

00:15:39.481 --> 00:15:40.607 position:50% align:center
[chuckles]

00:15:40.690 --> 00:15:41.900 position:50% align:center
[grunts]

00:15:46.071 --> 00:15:47.739 position:50% align:center
[MIZUKA laughs]

00:15:47.822 --> 00:15:50.575 position:50% align:center
You really are no
fun today. Too bad.

00:15:50.658 --> 00:15:53.119 position:50% align:center
[LICHT grunts]

00:15:53.203 --> 00:15:55.705 position:50% align:center
[MIZUKA] Did you forget
how my ability works?

00:15:55.789 --> 00:15:57.874 position:50% align:center
My Count is "persistence."

00:15:58.958 --> 00:16:00.919 position:50% align:center
No matter what obstacle
stands in their way

00:16:01.002 --> 00:16:02.837 position:50% align:center
or how long it may take,

00:16:02.921 --> 00:16:05.799 position:50% align:center
my shots trail their
mark till they hit!

00:16:05.882 --> 00:16:08.718 position:50% align:center
You can run, but you
can't hide, commander.

00:16:08.968 --> 00:16:13.306 position:50% align:center
[gasps, groans]

00:16:16.935 --> 00:16:18.520 position:50% align:center
[HINA]
Licht! I'm here!

00:16:18.603 --> 00:16:19.437 position:50% align:center
Hina!

00:16:19.521 --> 00:16:21.898 position:50% align:center
[gasps]

00:16:24.025 --> 00:16:25.485 position:50% align:center
[grunts]

00:16:25.568 --> 00:16:27.654 position:50% align:center
[grunts]

00:16:27.737 --> 00:16:30.949 position:50% align:center
[LICHT]
No. They're in... trouble.

00:16:32.450 --> 00:16:33.660 position:50% align:center
[gasps]

00:16:36.913 --> 00:16:39.207 position:50% align:center
Lynn! Snap out of it
and get moving!

00:16:39.290 --> 00:16:41.376 position:50% align:center
Pele... Watch out!

00:16:41.459 --> 00:16:42.794 position:50% align:center
[PELE grunts]

00:16:49.300 --> 00:16:52.095 position:50% align:center
[chuckles] I admit you're
gutsier than you look,

00:16:52.178 --> 00:16:54.389 position:50% align:center
though you don't look like much.

00:16:54.472 --> 00:16:56.391 position:50% align:center
[grunts]

00:16:56.474 --> 00:16:57.684 position:50% align:center
[LYNN grunts]

00:17:01.354 --> 00:17:03.606 position:50% align:center
[MIZUKA]
So. What should we do?

00:17:03.690 --> 00:17:06.151 position:50% align:center
Maybe we could kill the girl
who was worried about you.

00:17:06.234 --> 00:17:08.987 position:50% align:center
[grunts]
Please stop.

00:17:10.238 --> 00:17:13.908 position:50% align:center
You want to spare her life?
Then it's your turn to change.

00:17:13.992 --> 00:17:16.161 position:50% align:center
Revert back to the way you were.

00:17:16.244 --> 00:17:20.540 position:50% align:center
I can't do that. Just like I
can't bring myself to kill you.

00:17:20.623 --> 00:17:22.083 position:50% align:center
[gasps]

00:17:22.167 --> 00:17:26.463 position:50% align:center
It saddens me to hear that,
simply because I want to die.

00:17:26.546 --> 00:17:28.715 position:50% align:center
And I want it to be
at your skillful hands!

00:17:28.798 --> 00:17:30.050 position:50% align:center
[gasps]

00:17:30.133 --> 00:17:32.302 position:50% align:center
But I can't have this
version of you killing me.

00:17:32.385 --> 00:17:33.553 position:50% align:center
[LICHT grunts]

00:17:33.636 --> 00:17:34.971 position:50% align:center
[MIZUKA]
You're just a big ball of fluff

00:17:35.055 --> 00:17:37.474 position:50% align:center
so long as you're the
kind-hearted Rihito.

00:17:37.557 --> 00:17:39.059 position:50% align:center
[HINA]
Huh?

00:17:39.142 --> 00:17:41.728 position:50% align:center
Rihito? Who is that?

00:17:41.811 --> 00:17:43.438 position:50% align:center
[MIZUKA]
No more games.

00:17:46.566 --> 00:17:48.443 position:50% align:center
[MIZUKA] It's high time
you reclaimed your title

00:17:48.526 --> 00:17:50.320 position:50% align:center
as the Ace of Flashing Strikes.

00:17:50.403 --> 00:17:52.322 position:50% align:center
[LICHT]
Let him go.

00:17:52.405 --> 00:17:54.407 position:50% align:center
You know what my terms are.

00:17:54.491 --> 00:17:55.575 position:50% align:center
[TOWNSBOY A whimpers]

00:17:55.658 --> 00:17:58.203 position:50% align:center
[LICHT]
He has nothing to do with this!

00:17:58.286 --> 00:18:00.121 position:50% align:center
I just thought of something.

00:18:00.205 --> 00:18:02.457 position:50% align:center
What color flower do you
think he'd make if a bullet

00:18:02.540 --> 00:18:04.084 position:50% align:center
went straight through his head?

00:18:04.167 --> 00:18:06.419 position:50% align:center
I'm not sure why,
but the younger they are,

00:18:06.503 --> 00:18:08.213 position:50% align:center
the more beautiful their
blood tends to be!

00:18:08.296 --> 00:18:10.382 position:50% align:center
Sonohara. I'm begging you!

00:18:10.465 --> 00:18:12.384 position:50% align:center
[MIZUKA]
Oh, and he's very young.

00:18:12.467 --> 00:18:16.054 position:50% align:center
I'm getting giddy just thinking
about that bright crimson hue!

00:18:16.137 --> 00:18:17.097 position:50% align:center
What about you?

00:18:17.180 --> 00:18:19.724 position:50% align:center
I'm serious!

00:18:19.808 --> 00:18:22.227 position:50% align:center
Then prove it by
killing something.

00:18:22.310 --> 00:18:24.604 position:50% align:center
You realize if
you don't, I will.

00:18:24.688 --> 00:18:26.481 position:50% align:center
He's just a little boy!

00:18:26.564 --> 00:18:29.818 position:50% align:center
Yes. Let that anger
fester inside of you.

00:18:29.901 --> 00:18:32.445 position:50% align:center
Let it build until you have no
choice but to be consumed

00:18:32.529 --> 00:18:34.155 position:50% align:center
by your killer instincts!

00:18:34.239 --> 00:18:35.907 position:50% align:center
[MIZUKA laughs]

00:18:35.990 --> 00:18:38.576 position:50% align:center
Now. It really shouldn't
be this difficult.

00:18:38.660 --> 00:18:40.161 position:50% align:center
Just change back.

00:18:40.245 --> 00:18:42.789 position:50% align:center
Become the commander who killed
tens of thousands of enemies!

00:18:42.872 --> 00:18:44.874 position:50% align:center
The commander we all
loved to fear!

00:18:44.958 --> 00:18:47.877 position:50% align:center
Hurry and change! Please?
I want to see it!

00:18:47.961 --> 00:18:50.463 position:50% align:center
Look at me. Don't be scared.

00:18:50.547 --> 00:18:53.466 position:50% align:center
It'll be fine, because I'm
gonna save you.

00:18:58.555 --> 00:19:01.975 position:50% align:center
[LICHT]
Hey... Seriously.

00:19:02.058 --> 00:19:05.979 position:50% align:center
You're gonna make it
outta this. I promise.

00:19:06.062 --> 00:19:09.482 position:50% align:center
So don't even sweat it.

00:19:09.566 --> 00:19:12.819 position:50% align:center
Mama! Where's my mommy?

00:19:12.902 --> 00:19:14.070 position:50% align:center
I want my mommy!

00:19:14.154 --> 00:19:15.697 position:50% align:center
[MIZUKA] Even the kid
knows that's a promise

00:19:15.780 --> 00:19:18.116 position:50% align:center
you can't possibly keep.

00:19:18.199 --> 00:19:20.744 position:50% align:center
Not as Rihito.

00:19:20.827 --> 00:19:23.121 position:50% align:center
Time to end this.

00:19:23.204 --> 00:19:26.791 position:50% align:center
[TOWNSBOY A]
I want my mommy! I'm scared!

00:19:26.875 --> 00:19:30.420 position:50% align:center
Mommy help me!

00:19:30.503 --> 00:19:33.548 position:50% align:center
[gunshot]

00:19:37.469 --> 00:19:38.970 position:50% align:center
What's this?

00:19:42.265 --> 00:19:43.475 position:50% align:center
[gasps]

00:19:45.602 --> 00:19:46.853 position:50% align:center
[PELE gasps]

00:19:49.773 --> 00:19:51.441 position:50% align:center
[LICHT]
I told you to stop.

00:19:53.651 --> 00:19:56.029 position:50% align:center
You refused several times.

00:20:00.116 --> 00:20:02.660 position:50% align:center
[LICHT]
You want me to kill you?

00:20:02.744 --> 00:20:05.538 position:50% align:center
Stay put and you'll
get your wish.

00:20:05.622 --> 00:20:07.832 position:50% align:center
No, Licht! Don't give in!

00:20:07.916 --> 00:20:09.459 position:50% align:center
You stay out of this.

00:20:09.542 --> 00:20:10.752 position:50% align:center
[NANA gasps]

00:20:12.420 --> 00:20:14.214 position:50% align:center
I'll kill her.

00:20:15.840 --> 00:20:17.300 position:50% align:center
[LICHT]
Hina.

00:20:17.384 --> 00:20:21.846 position:50% align:center
You asked me if I had a dream.
And I told you I had a goal.

00:20:21.930 --> 00:20:24.891 position:50% align:center
[LICHT] Jail. You asked
me who I really am.

00:20:24.974 --> 00:20:26.142 position:50% align:center
Truth is...

00:20:26.226 --> 00:20:27.811 position:50% align:center
[LYNN, PELE gasp]

00:20:32.440 --> 00:20:33.650 position:50% align:center
[LICHT]
...I am...

00:20:35.443 --> 00:20:37.153 position:50% align:center
[LICHT]
...The Plunderer.

00:20:42.909 --> 00:20:44.828 position:50% align:center
[gasps]

00:20:46.955 --> 00:20:49.457 position:50% align:center
[LICHT] And my goal is to
take everything this nation

00:20:49.541 --> 00:20:51.042 position:50% align:center
has to offer.

00:20:51.126 --> 00:20:52.877 position:50% align:center
Everything.

00:22:36.648 --> 00:22:38.108 position:50% align:center
[LICHT]
Man, that was seriously heavy!

00:22:38.191 --> 00:22:40.443 position:50% align:center
I must've gotten some serious
karma for not being serious

00:22:40.527 --> 00:22:41.986 position:50% align:center
enough during the previews.

00:22:42.070 --> 00:22:44.531 position:50% align:center
Never too late for a change,
so I'll be serious from now on!

00:22:44.614 --> 00:22:48.493 position:50% align:center
[NANA] Next episode, "Serious."
Way to atone before you die.

00:22:48.576 --> 00:22:49.994 position:50% align:center
[LICHT]
Huh? Seriously?